close_reason: Fixed via readBoolOption. Verified --dry-run writes nothing (before=0 after=0).
body: "Bug class #1 (option-key normalization). Runtime normalizes --dry-run to dryRun; handler read ctx.options[\"dry-run\"] (always undefined).\nRepro: pm todos import TODO.md --dry-run\nObserved: actually imported 5 items (before=0 after=5), printed \"Imported 5\". Exit 0.\nExpected: write nothing, print [dry-run] previews.\nFix: added readBoolOption(options,\"dry-run\",\"dryRun\"). Verified before=0 after=0, prints [dry-run] previews."
